    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Eumarinemobius sundaicus Gorochov & Tan, 2018 or Marinemobius asahinai (Yamasaki, 1979) female: habitus in dorsal view (A), anterior part of body in lateral view (B), face in anterior view (C), subgenital plate in ventral view (D), ovipositor at the apex in dorsal (E) and lateral (F) views. Scale bars: 2 mm (A); 1 mm (B, C, E, F); 0.5 mm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3149789/files/figure.png" ;
